parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering lock module can cause the vehicle to become inoperable, leaving the driver stranded and potentially in a dangerous situation.
symptoms: The vehicle will not start
the steering wheel is locked
the key indicator and steering lock indicator on the dashboard are illuminated
the push-to-start button reads "LOCK"
and the vehicle may require towing.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the front suspension can cause the vehicle to become unstable, leading to loss of control and potential accidents.
symptoms: The front suspension has caused the tire to come off
the bracket that attaches to the strut bar has broken off
the front right wheel has come loose while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ESCL can cause the vehicle to not start, leaving the driver stranded, and potentially leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle will not start
the "No Key Detected" warning light is illuminated
the push-button ignition does not respond
the key fob is not recognized by the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the push-button start system can cause the vehicle to not start, leaving the driver stranded, and potentially leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle will not start
the push-button ignition does not respond
the key fob is not recognized by the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission and speed sensor can cause the vehicle to suddenly lose power, jerk, or stall, potentially leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly loses power
jerks
or stalls
the speedometer and odometer do not function properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause the airbags to not deploy in the event of an accident, potentially leading to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
the passenger airbag sensor is faulty.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the passenger airbag sensor can cause the airbag to malfunction, leading to potential injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The passenger airbag light blinks or remains illuminated
indicating that the airbag is off or malfunctioning
even when a passenger is present in the seat.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The illumination of the airbag warning light can indicate a malfunction in the airbag system, which can lead to potential injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated on the dashboard
indicating a problem with the airbag system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the occupant sensor can cause the airbag to malfunction, leading to potential injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The passenger airbag light blinks or remains illuminated
indicating that the airbag is off or malfunctioning
even when a passenger is present in the seat.
